y during it?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: O Allah, You are pardoning. You love to forgive, so forgive me.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24610,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/05\/pens-dried-qadr-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14646,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Pens have dried upon Allah&#8217;s decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty created His creation in darkness and He cast over them His light. Whoever is touched by that light is guided, and whoever misses it is led astray. Thus, I say the pens\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/haram-silver-gold-dishware\/","url_meta":{"origin":14646,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Extravagance: Silver and gold dishes, cutlery forbidden","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever drinks from a vessel of gold or silver, surely he has only filled his belly with the fire of Hell.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5634, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2065 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32706,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/all-cures-but-aging\/","url_meta":{"origin":14646,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah placed cures for all diseases, except aging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: A bedouin said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not seek treatment?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes, O servants of Allah, seek treatment. Verily, Allah did not place a disease but that he also placed its treatment or cure, except for one ailment.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10010,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/25\/qadr-dua-repel-divine-decree\/","url_meta":{"origin":14646,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication repels the divine decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing repels the divine decree but supplication, and nothing increases life span but righteousness.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2139 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u00a0Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u